  "title": "6 months Accounts Executive ($4000) #HJO",
  "description": "<p>Jobscope </p><ul><li>Assist with daily accounting operations such as data entry, filing, and record keeping</li><li>Process invoices, payments, and receipts accurately and on time</li><li>Support accounts payable and accounts receivable functions</li><li>Reconcile bank statements and track expenses</li><li>Prepare basic financial reports and summaries</li><li>Assist in month-end closing activities</li><li>Maintain proper documentation for audits and compliance</li><li>Liaise with internal teams and external vendors on billing or payment matters</li><li>Perform general administrative support for the finance team</li></ul><p>Requirements <br /></p><ul><li>Min Diploma in Accountancy / Any related course of studies </li><li>Min 2 years of experience in Accounting <br /></li></ul><p>Interested candidates are invited to email your resume to:</p><p>jen.ooi@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p>Jenalyn Ooi Huai Sian (R1765551)</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd  | Company Reg. No. 199601303W | EA License Number: 99C4599</p><p><br /></p>",
